  "texts": [
    "Towards the semantic misalignment problem in existing MLLMs when processing contextually different images, we introduce the bidirectional semantic guidance mechanism in the image perception stage.",
    "It comprises two interactive processes, including Part A: Assisted Visual Token Extraction and Part B: Contextual Semantic Generation.",
    "Initially, in Part A, the Q-former layers are applied to process the currently perceived image based on the natural language query and extract the initial visual tokens h 𝑖.",
    "Next, in Part B, we propose a novel visual tokenizer called W-former.",
    "Guided by initial visual tokens h 𝑖, W-former extracts synchronous contextual semantics c 𝑖 from contextual images (i.e., images other than the currently perceived image)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}